{
  "stem": "9489.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I remember that in school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So they burned his room with him together, not to spread these bacteria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And this was in Bukhara.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I can swear for it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So then, [SIGHS] when we finished the courses, this-- me-- I-- with these guys, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They disappeared, the Jewish boys.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When they-- when they finished the-- the university, they disappear.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Each went for himself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I went with the school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They sent us to Magnitogorsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't-- I didn't want to play smart.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They send us Magnitogorsk, to build [INAUDIBLE] to build the ovens for steel.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You understand I'm talking?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "To make the tank steel, to produce.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like, we were finished engineering, so we come there, they treat us like kings.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They give us underground bungalows, nice food, winter clothes, and they send us to build number two, number three, number four [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That is the ovens for to make steel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we specialize in foundation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got other groups-- older people, and they-- we-- they dig for us the bulldozers, and we put in the two-by-four, the wood, for the cement to pour for the foundation, and the steel bars.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's all what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And how large a group were you?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were lots-- lots.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was lots adults.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was lots of adults.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But our-- our boss was-- our leader, with a beard-- he was from the aristocrats.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "From the-- from the king, from the czar, from Russia, the aristocrat?",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He explain us who he is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was in the jail, but when the war started, they let him in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was an engineer from-- from Moscow.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't-- sure, you know?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived together.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told all his life story, what in jail, everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anyways, he was our leader.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
